=head1 NAME

_FIND_BAD_PIXELS_ARRAY_TESTS_ - Find bad pixels for array test sequences.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive provides a wrapper for _FIND_BAD_PIXELS_ for array test
sequence processing. If the current frame has been set up with an internal
header in _ARRAY_TESTS_STEER_, then bad pixels will be found.

=head1 ARGUMENTS

None.

=head1 TASKS

None.

=head1 AUTHORS

Brad Cavanagh <b.cavanagh@jach.hawaii.edu> (JAC)

=head1 COPYRIGHT

Copyright (C) 1998-2002 Particle Physics and Astronomy Research
Council. All Rights Reserved.

=cut

if($Frm->uhdr("ARRAY_TESTS_FIND_BAD_PIXELS")) {
  _FIND_BAD_PIXELS_
}
